lead_paragraph: Arsenal have only themselves to blame after a run of two wins in nine games in all competitions has left them with only an outside chance of winning any silverware, midfielder Mesut Ozil was quoted as saying on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: We Messed Up Our Season, Says Arsenal's Ozil
headline.main: We Messed Up Our Season, Says Arsenal's Ozil
